<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{language}}">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HDD Fixer - {{status}}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
        .content { padding: 30px; }
        .status-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 8px 16px; background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0; }
        .order-info { background: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { background: #f3f4f6; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #2563eb; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🔧 HDD FIXER</h1>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9;">Сервисный центр</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2 style="color: #1f2937; margin-top: 0;">{{#if (eq language 'ru')}}
                Статус заказа изменён
            {{else if (eq language 'en')}}
                Order status changed
            {{else}}
                Buyurtma holati o'zgardi
            {{/if}}</h2>
            
            <p style="color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                {{#if (eq language 'ru')}}
                    Здравствуйте, <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>!
                {{else if (eq language 'en')}}
                    Hello, <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>!
                {{else}}
                    Assalomu alaykum, <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>!
                {{/if}}
            </p>
            
            <div class="status-badge">
                📋 {{status}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="order-info">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
                    {{#if (eq language 'ru')}}
                        Номер заказа
                    {{else if (eq language 'en')}}
                        Order number
                    {{else}}
                        Buyurtma raqami
                    {{/if}}
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #1f2937;">
                    #{{orderId}}
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                {{#if (eq language 'ru')}}
                    Вы можете просмотреть детальную информацию о заказе в личном кабинете.
                {{else if (eq language 'en')}}
                    You can view detailed order information in your dashboard.
                {{else}}
                    Batafsil ma'lumotni shaxsiy kabinetingizda ko'rishingiz mumkin.
                {{/if}}
            </p>
            
            <a href="https://hdd-fixer.uz/orders/{{orderId}}" class="button" style="display: inline-block;">
                {{#if (eq language 'ru')}}
                    Перейти к заказу
                {{else if (eq language 'en')}}
                    View Order
                {{else}}
                    Buyurtmaga o'tish
                {{/if}}
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p style="margin: 0;">© 2024 HDD Fixer. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px;">
                {{#if (eq language 'ru')}}
                    Это автоматическое уведомление, пожалуйста, не отвечайте на него.
                {{else if (eq language 'en')}}
                    This is an automated notification, please do not reply.
                {{else}}
                    Bu avtomatik bildirishnoma, javob yubormang.
                {{/if}}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
